$$Nmc     3
$$corrMod gaussian
$$margiFirst gaussian
$corrL
   1.0 1.0 1.0
$$fieldAvg
   0.0
$$fieldVar
   1.0
$$method
   1


!

INPUTS ###########################
<OPTION>: <DESCRIPTION> -> <TYPE> [: <OPTIONS>]

Nmc: number of Monte Carlo realizations -> integer
corrMod: correlation model -> text : gaussian
margiFirst : first order marginal law  -> text : gaussian, lognormal
corrL : correlation length vector XYZ -> nDimensions double
fieldAvg : field average vector XYZ -> nDimensions double
fieldVar : field variance vector XYZ -> nDimensions double
method: method of field generation -> <integer> : 1 for Isotropic, 2 for Shinozuka

FILE SYNTAX RULES ###########################

$$Scalar_Name For scalar entries
$Vector_Name  For vector entries
Comments are in between two exclamation points 

!
